Package uw.rfpk.servlets

Class Summary
AbortJob This servlet aborts the job specified by the client.
DiffFiles This servlet compares two text files and sends back the differences in unix format.
ExitMDATest This servlet invalidates the session.
GetArchive This servlet sends back the version's text of model or dataset that was selected by the user from version list by the immediately previous call to the servlet GetVersions.
GetGroupUsers This servlet sends back the usernames of a specified group in a Vector object.
GetHistory This servlet sends back information of events occured in the job's processing histry.
GetInput This servlet seads back the three components: source, data, model of the SPK input file.
GetJnlp This servlet receives five parameters: host, port, secret, jnlp_dir and type.
GetJobArchive This servlet sends back either the model or the dataset that is used by the job.
GetJobInfo This servlet sends back job information including model, dataset, method and parent.
GetLastVersion This servlet sends bsck the revision number of the model or datsset requested by the client.
GetOutput This servlet sends back the job's output including source, report, job, model and dataset.
GetVersions This servlet sends bsck the version list of the model or datsset that was selected by the user from model list by the immediately previous call to the servlet UserModels or from dataset list by the immediately previous call to the servlet UserDatasets.
InitMDATest This servlet is for test only.
SetJobAbstract This servlet sets the job abstract specified by the client.
SetJobShareWith This servlet sets the job share_with field of the job specified by the client.
SubmitJob This servlet assemblies and then submits the job, the model and the dataset to the database.
TestConnection This servlet is to test the connection between the Model Design Agent and the associated web server and get the content of the method table from the database for MDA.
UserDatasets This servlet sends back information about a list of datasets belonging to a specified user.
UserJobs This servlet sends back information about a list of jobs belonging to the specified user.
UserModels This servlet sends back information about a list of models belonging to a specified user.
